---------------------------------------------
React Notes
---------------------------------------------
React is a js library originated from Facebook adn went Open Source in March 2013.
Twttier Netflix Microsoft uses React.
JSX - JavaScript XML
---------------------------------------------
How to Inplement Babel
---------------------------------------------
This would go in the head of the page >>>>>>>
<script 
  src = "unpkg.com/babel-standalone@6/babel.min.js" crossorigin>
</script>
---------------------------------------------
Creating react application and run
---------------------------------------------
To create a react app one would type into the Terminal: >>>>>>>>>>
  npx create-react-app your-project-name
"npm start" to run it
---------------------------------------------
Functions
---------------------------------------------
UseState() is used for handling state variables
to import useState you would enter >>>>>> 
  import {useState} from 'react'
onChange() can be used to listen if any changes are made and run the function.
